     H            Y.
      ** KFAR2B *****************************************************
      * PRINT ALL ITEM SIGNAL KANBAN LOCATION  ON BARCODE           *
      * PROGRAM ID. : KFAR2B                                        *
      * CREATE DATE. : JAN/30/01                                    *
      ******************************************* KFAR2B ************
     FKFAWP2A UF  E                    DISK
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PPROC   1
     C*
     C                     SETOF                     90
     C           1         SETLLKFAWP2A
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     READ KFAWP2A                  90
     C   90                LEAVE
     C           KZYJRS    IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE '2'       KZYJRS
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           PPROC     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVEL' '       KZBRCD
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     UPDATKFAWP201
     C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C*
